latestIgtvVideos.title: Proud of u mom : a born Rajasthani dancer❤
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Looks easy, isn't it?
I remember my mom performed this dance after rehearsing for just one time in night, coz she cudn't spare more time from her hectic schedule (that of an amazing house wife). 
She is extremely talented when it comes to performing on stage. But I am yet awestruck to see how she could hold such a heavy matka (full of sand) with such an ease while dancing with that flawless body language nd expressions, nd she even sat with it, didn't u notice? 
I couldn't even lift this "matka", while trying to imitate her. 
I'mma proud daughter @poojajoshi178 😚❤👏🏻
Drop down ur views ;)

latestIgtvVideos.title: Journey of my Angel
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
6 August 2014, the day that changed our lives, the day when my elder sister met with an accident, followed by a brain clot and spinal injury, and lost her lower body sensation and memory, thereafter. 

From that day to today, there hasn't been a single day where she hasn't impressed me with her hard work and dedication to make her career, despite of the challenges and struggles that fate brought to her. 
A big thanks to Delhi Para Sports Association for making this platform wherein inspirational souls like my own sister get to dream of and be an athlete, despite of being specially abled. 

I fall at lack of words to describe how excited I am for her journey. 
I am so so proud of you @shriya_newlife for you have fought so hard to become a para Athlete
for u didn't leave a stone unturned to become what u aimed to
for ur determination and hard work was and is always way past ur potential
for u have way to go, and I know you are meant to shine bright and brighter ❤
. 
. 
#delhiparasports
